WEBVTT

00:00:00.518 --> 00:00:07.119
Good morning, family. Praise the Lord. Thank you for joining me today. Well, we're so focused on the war stuff.

00:00:07.120 --> 00:00:14.048
We're so focused on what's going on over there in Israel and all this other stuff that we're forgetting that He said He's going to shake the heavens.

00:00:14.049 --> 00:00:27.438
He's going to shake the earth. He's going to shake the politics, and He's going to shake the finances. There were five major things He said He was about to shake.

00:00:27.439 --> 00:00:37.474
And I'm telling you all, there's a major earthquake that's about to take place from British Columbia all the way down to about San Francisco.

00:00:37.475 --> 00:00:50.623
I saw a major earthquake that's about to take place there. I saw a tsunami wave coming in even into Alaska—something major. And I even told everybody what the Lord told me.

00:00:50.624 --> 00:00:59.636
He said, "Watch what's in the water."Many people, because it's out of sight, out of mind, are not paying attention to what's in the water.

00:00:59.637 --> 00:01:11.776
And there will be signs in the days ahead of gases, things, and fish from the depth coming up from the bottom that we've never seen before.

00:01:11.777 --> 00:01:18.239
All around the world, dead fish will come up from the bottom. They'll go, "What is this?

00:01:18.240 --> 00:01:27.135
We've never seen it."But it will come up to the top, and things will die on the beaches, and you're going to see things and they'll go, "Where did this come from? Where did these whales come from?

00:01:27.136 --> 00:01:35.651
Where's this stuff come from?"Because folks, there's stuff that we've never even known existed down there because we've only explored so much of our oceans.

00:01:35.652 --> 00:01:43.519
But I'm telling you by the spirit of the Lord, what He's told me is we're about to see pressure on the earth's crust.

00:01:43.520 --> 00:01:47.840
There's something that's interfering with it in outer space.

00:01:47.841 --> 00:02:02.135
There's something in our galaxy that is interfering with our planet right now that's causing a shifting and a shaking of our earth's crust with the magma and all the lava and all the stuff.

00:02:02.136 --> 00:02:06.761
And I'm telling you, it's the gases; it's all the pressure of the earth.

00:02:06.762 --> 00:02:13.848
And to relieve the pressure from what's happening on our earth's crust, we're going to see earthquakes like we've never seen before.

00:02:13.849 --> 00:02:20.495
And we're going to see volcanoes like we've never even seen before in this generation, up to probably a thousand years.

00:02:20.496 --> 00:02:29.217
I don't know; I just know that this is going to be a worldwide shaking.

00:02:29.218 --> 00:02:34.479
It's not just about America, but it's going to be even about Japan. A major earthquake in Japan.

00:02:34.480 --> 00:02:44.784
Major earthquakes in these areas that you go, "Oh my God."And people are going to see it on the news and they're going to wake up the next day, and I saw even 50,000 people in British Columbia die.

00:02:44.785 --> 00:02:57.439
50,000 people. I saw the number, and I saw major buildings falling. I saw major skyscrapers just tipping over—major shaking.

00:02:57.440 --> 00:03:01.937
And so you say, "Brandon, well, that just scares me."It's not for you to be in fear.

00:03:01.938 --> 00:03:05.631
A thousand shall fall at your side and 10,000 at your right hand.

00:03:05.632 --> 00:03:09.940
If you're watching this channel, you're in the right place because I believe in the covenant.

00:03:09.941 --> 00:03:16.828
I believe just like we have these big storms where they say, "Well, they're going to have tornadoes, everything,"no, we take authority over tornadoes.

00:03:16.829 --> 00:03:21.893
We don't allow tornadoes around this area. We take our authority in this part.

00:03:21.894 --> 00:03:31.983
And I say, "As long as I have dominion and authority—I don't know how far my authority goes out there"—and I'll teach you all this as we go, but you have authority over your neighborhood.

00:03:31.984 --> 00:03:37.023
And that's why I drive around. I drive around and pray wherever I put my feet.

00:03:37.024 --> 00:03:42.878
I start pleading the blood and protecting things, going around schools and doing things what God's called me to do to protect.

00:03:42.879 --> 00:03:49.029
I say, "No, we're not going to have any major events or hurting people around here."You moved me to this area.

00:03:49.030 --> 00:03:57.114
I used to do it over where I was in Guthrie, but God said, "I'm moving you out of that area."And He moved us to Tulsa.

00:03:57.115 --> 00:04:03.221
And now we drive around in Tulsa and we pray over the Tulsa area calling for revival. We drive around.

00:04:03.222 --> 00:04:08.502
I even go in front of that painting a lot and stay in that neighborhood and pray for revival.

00:04:08.503 --> 00:04:15.119
But I go there because I'm looking for revival. It's time to get serious.

00:04:15.120 --> 00:04:21.518
It's time to get serious and expect God to show up and show off in your life.

00:04:21.519 --> 00:04:29.643
It's time to quit playing church, going and having prayer groups and just expecting a normal prayer group.

00:04:29.644 --> 00:04:40.153
I'm talking let the Holy Ghost show up and pray through you so much so that we're changing the nations.

00:04:40.154 --> 00:04:49.156
That's what I pray every single time I do this. I said, "God, let it not be me at all, but let You show up."If it's me, I won't put it out.

00:04:49.156 --> 00:04:55.943
I said, "Just erase it, Braden. It's just trash."Because if the Holy Spirit isn't there, I'm not there.

00:04:55.944 --> 00:04:57.903
And it's just me making content. I'm not here to make content for entertainment.

00:04:57.904 --> 00:05:00.662
If I don't feel a move of the Holy Ghost in a river flow, I'm not releasing it because I'm not here to entertain you.

00:05:00.663 --> 00:05:07.194
We're here to change nations. And people say, "Well, just put it out anyway."No, I'm not.

00:05:07.195 --> 00:05:15.124
Like I said, this is a major calling to me. This isn't a job; this is a calling.

00:05:15.125 --> 00:05:25.918
And people say, "Well, you know, it's not made for you to understand."This is what God's called me to do, and this is what I'm supposed to do is bring prayer to you.

00:05:25.919 --> 00:05:31.918
And I told Him, I said, "Lord, I'm submitted unto You."So I get still until He speaks.

00:05:31.919 --> 00:05:41.488
I make a video every day, and if I don't feel it, I don't release it. If I get up and I tell Brad, "That's trash.

00:05:41.489 --> 00:05:52.929
I'm not releasing that,"it's because if I don't feel the power of the Holy Ghost flowing through it, I refuse to waste your time.

00:05:52.930 --> 00:06:03.472
And that's why I feel like people should be at church. If you don't feel the Holy Ghost, sit down.

00:06:03.473 --> 00:06:16.799
We've got to get more desperate for Him. And in doing so, He will show up. He will show up in your desperation.

00:06:16.800 --> 00:06:38.318
I was out power washing the side of my house, and me—I'm going to say this, and you don't know me, but a lot of people think they do—I was power washing my house and I said, "Lord, if I could just have Your help to fix my water line over there, that's all I want to ask You."I was just trying to be humble, like I didn't want to bother Him.

00:06:38.319 --> 00:06:43.714
And He said, "Brandon, I want to be involved in every area of your life.

00:06:43.715 --> 00:06:51.198
Nothing is ever too big and nothing is ever too small for Me to want to be involved with it all.

00:06:51.199 --> 00:07:16.712
I want to be involved in every area of your life."In other words, He said to me, "So you think you can do it on your own on the other things?"When I was power washing, I said, "Well, I don't really need You to help me power wash the house, but I really need help with that water thing over there."But He said, "You think you can do it on your own?

00:07:16.713 --> 00:07:27.996
You can't do nothing on your own. Everything you do, everything you think about, you need Me and you don't even realize it.

00:07:27.997 --> 00:07:39.055
And I'm an ever-present help in a time of need. Everything you do and everything you speak, everything about you, Brandon, you need Me.

00:07:39.056 --> 00:07:46.959
The moment you try to separate yourself from Me is separating yourself from the vine, and there's death in it.

00:07:46.960 --> 00:08:10.638
I am everything. I am all in all. Do you understand? There is nothing that you can do apart from Me, even power washing this house."I started to weep.

00:08:10.639 --> 00:08:20.959
I looked at the ground while I was power washing. I was so frustrated that day because we've had a really hard time.

00:08:20.960 --> 00:08:32.616
And I said, "God, help me to never think that I can do anything without You."I didn't want to bother Him, but I said, "Lord, if You could just help me with this water line thing.

00:08:32.617 --> 00:08:45.466
I'm having a real hard time here, and I need help."I can take care of this. I can handle it.

00:08:45.467 --> 00:09:02.879
I don't really need you over here on this, but if you could really help me out, just shaking me and making me realize that there's nothing I can do without him.

00:09:02.880 --> 00:09:13.463
Washing a dog, cleaning, mowing my grass whenever it's so high because of all the issues that we've had.

00:09:13.464 --> 00:09:21.278
Walking in every area of your life, being desperate for him to show up in every area.

00:09:21.279 --> 00:09:31.493
Even the things that you don't think that he wants to be involved in, he wants to be involved in. It doesn't matter what it is; he wants to be involved in it.

00:09:31.494 --> 00:09:41.629
And that's the place of desperation—allowing the Holy Spirit to move in every area of your life. And that's where I was asking him.

00:09:41.630 --> 00:10:09.528
I said, "Oh, so you feel you can do it without me?"It checked me really hard because I thought, "Well, of course, I don't need you to power wash the house."And you think you can do it without me?

00:10:09.529 --> 00:10:25.124
In all that you do, in word and in deed, do all for the glory of God. All that you do, all for the glory of God. I was challenged.

00:10:25.125 --> 00:10:34.350
I listened to what's in these life lessons, you know, with me planting flowers when he said to me, "You just arranged it.

00:10:34.351 --> 00:10:41.970
I caused the flowers to grow. I caused the earth to produce and put pressure on the seed.

00:10:41.971 --> 00:10:52.149
I caused the rain to fall on it. I was the one that was ahead of all of it, Brandon. And all you did was organize them.

00:10:52.150 --> 00:11:01.119
And I even gave you the wisdom to do that."Everything you do, there's nothing apart from me.

00:11:01.120 --> 00:11:10.639
Everything that you do is only through me. And in that, I am learning.

00:11:10.640 --> 00:11:15.090
When you think, "I'm a man, I can do this. I'm a man, I can fix my car.

00:11:15.091 --> 00:11:27.083
I'm a man, I can mow my grass."It's like, "Daddy, I don't need you to help tie my shoes anymore. I'm big now. You don't pick out my clothes anymore.

00:11:27.084 --> 00:11:35.679
I can pick my own clothes out, daddy."But even in that, listening to him and saying, "Father, I don't want to get dressed without you.

00:11:35.680 --> 00:11:42.157
What do you feel I should wear today?"Involving him in every area of your life.

00:11:42.158 --> 00:11:47.039
"Lord, I need you to tell me how to make my marriage stronger today.

00:11:47.040 --> 00:11:59.806
I need you to tell me how to be a better father to my children."No matter how many books I think I could read or whatever, it all is based solely out of him.

00:11:59.807 --> 00:12:12.471
And I know I don't want to keep going over this, but it's so important that I drive it home to you that he wants to be all in and all to you in every area of your life.

00:12:12.472 --> 00:12:23.573
And so as we see these things in the economy, I told you we do not let up off of things in prayer until we make it a greasy spot.

00:12:23.574 --> 00:12:33.119
You may see a little victory and a lot of people just go, "Well, we saw the first blade, then the ear,"and people go, "Well, we can let it go through prayer.

00:12:33.120 --> 00:12:39.679
We don't have to attack it anymore."That's whenever you hit it harder and you hit it until it's a greasy spot.

00:12:39.680 --> 00:12:47.039
So, we see a judge. Everything's fine with XRP. Everything looks great. She goes and starts going against it.

00:12:47.040 --> 00:12:57.797
Instantaneously, people go, "Oh my gosh, the sky is falling with XRP again."And I said, "Isn't it amazing the very things the Lord tells us to pray over?"People give up on it and you let go of the rope.

00:12:57.798 --> 00:13:08.990
And then the enemy's there and he's doing tug-of-war and he goes and he tries to pull the rug right out from underneath you instantaneously because the body of Christ goes and pulls and goes, "Look, we won."And then the devil's like...

00:13:08.991 --> 00:13:16.958
and he pulls it and everybody goes, "Well, what happened there?"You didn't keep on keeping on.

00:13:16.959 --> 00:13:24.239
You underestimated your enemy. And that's what happens. It happens a lot with the body of Christ.

00:13:24.240 --> 00:13:31.902
Same thing we do with President Trump. We won. We won. Oh, good. We won. Oh, November! Woohoo!

00:13:31.903 --> 00:13:36.479
And now the Lord starts talking to me and said, "Brandon, are you going to pray for his safety?

00:13:36.480 --> 00:13:45.803
What's going on?"There's more things here that you need to understand, that there's more attacks on his life, attempts on his life. You need to pray for him.

00:13:45.804 --> 00:13:55.679
So, I'll just be doing my own thing and then the Lord told me, and I see more attempts—like it was with the ear—in the days ahead, worse.

00:13:55.680 --> 00:14:04.345
And we have FBI agents calling 86ing 47, and we see people calling for him to be removed and doing all this stuff.

00:14:04.346 --> 00:14:10.470
Well, I'm just saying I want him to be put in prison. That's not what he was saying.

00:14:10.471 --> 00:14:14.853
You have people that are threatening his life on a day-to-day basis, even in upper government.

00:14:14.854 --> 00:14:24.441
And I've told you all, if you don't pray for this man, he can't do it without help.

00:14:24.442 --> 00:14:29.817
No, it's time for the body of Christ to get more serious than what we've ever been serious before.

00:14:29.818 --> 00:14:38.073
And let's drive this thing home. Let's finish our race. Finish. Go long. Live long and finish strong.

00:14:38.074 --> 00:14:44.030
We need to live long and finish strong and finish our race with great victory until we get on the other side.

00:14:44.031 --> 00:14:48.053
And when we get over on the other side, then we take a break and we do our victory lap.

00:14:48.054 --> 00:14:53.439
We do our victory lap. We do our victory dance. I don't know what else to say.

00:14:53.440 --> 00:14:58.159
But until then, we are on battle mode. We've got our shield up.

00:14:58.160 --> 00:15:04.246
We're not looking at our enemy and going, "Well, he's already lost."Yeah, he's already lost.

00:15:04.247 --> 00:15:13.039
But we stay in a state of war with our sword and our shield in our hand going, "Hey, where's another devil?

00:15:13.040 --> 00:15:25.198
I'm going to cut this devil's head off and I'm going to keep warring against him."Because the moment you take your eye off your enemy, he's there ready to devour you.

00:15:25.199 --> 00:15:31.354
That's just the end times. You know why? Let me tell you why. Because he has a sense of urgency.

00:15:31.355 --> 00:15:40.045
What's his urgency? He knows his time is short. He has a sense of urgency. So where's the body of Christ's urgency right now?

00:15:40.046 --> 00:15:46.216
Well, you know, it's not convenient to go to prayer group on Sunday nights after church.

00:15:46.217 --> 00:15:57.359
So you have, you know, 20 people show up out of a church of over a thousand. That is pathetic. Where's the sense of urgency?

00:15:57.360 --> 00:16:04.805
You have the elders; you have the gray hairs in there—the people who are the pillars of the church that have been there—but the young people, they don't care.

00:16:04.806 --> 00:16:22.239
"I got to watch American Idol."Do you understand? If we do not pray it out in the spirit, it will never happen in the natural.

00:16:22.240 --> 00:16:30.074
You think that you get spiritual breakthrough just because it's just supposed to happen?

00:16:30.075 --> 00:16:36.799
It happens birthed out of the spirit first. Healings, demonstrations, manifestation.

00:16:36.800 --> 00:16:49.431
Azusa Street came out of major prayer first. Pensacola revival of John Kilpatrick came out of two years of intercessory prayer. Two years of praying.

00:16:49.432 --> 00:16:59.888
I don't know if it was twice a week or once a week, but they prayed and they did that for two years, and then on Father's Day, bam, the glory fell.

00:16:59.889 --> 00:17:07.537
Two years they prayed for revival. Azusa Street, I think it was like four years; William Seymour and them, they prayed in a little house.

00:17:07.538 --> 00:17:10.159
They prayed and prayed and prayed, and then God gave them a word.

00:17:10.160 --> 00:17:22.798
There was a great earthquake and it shook San Francisco, and then because they gave that prophetic word, people were going, "Who gave that accurate prophetic word?"and the glory showed up and they had to move it into a barn.

00:17:22.799 --> 00:17:34.479
God will show up in the most unlikely places. He shows up in a place of desperation.

00:17:34.480 --> 00:17:39.634
He shows up with the people who are desperate and hungry. He'll show up in a stable.

00:17:39.635 --> 00:17:48.141
Remember, he'll show up in a stable in a place where barn animals are—not fit for a king.

00:17:48.142 --> 00:17:54.239
But he shows up in a place of humility, not a place of arrogance.

00:17:54.240 --> 00:18:07.458
People who are arrogant leading prayer, people who are arrogant preaching at the church thinking, "Well, I've got my PhD.""I've got all this."Do you not know how many people have prophesied over me?

00:18:07.459 --> 00:18:15.918
Do you know how many people have imparted into me? Who cares?

00:18:15.919 --> 00:18:22.153
God resists the proud and exalts the humble. God exalts the humble.

00:18:22.154 --> 00:18:29.595
And the moment you have an attitude or an arrogant look, thinking like, "I can do this house without you, Lord.

00:18:29.596 --> 00:18:38.802
I don't need your help with that. I need this over there"—the moment you realize how much you have to learn, it's time to humble you.

00:18:38.803 --> 00:18:50.492
And I realize there is nothing outside of him. Even power washing a house, there is nothing outside of him.

00:18:50.493 --> 00:18:57.216
And many people feel they've got this. You don't have anything. You don't have anything.

00:18:57.217 --> 00:19:06.959
I can leave prayer, and the Lord told me, he said, "Baby, you can fake the anointing for so long until people will catch on.

00:19:06.960 --> 00:19:18.541
You can run on fumes, son for a while, but eventually people will catch on. There is nothing outside of me. I am the vine.

00:19:18.542 --> 00:19:24.630
You are the branch."That's why Jesus said, "I say nothing without hearing what my father says.

00:19:24.631 --> 00:19:33.532
I do nothing without doing what my father tells me to do."Because he realized there was a desperation in seeking his father on a day-to-day basis.

00:19:33.533 --> 00:19:42.159
And he was the Son of God, and he realized there was nothing he could do in this earth without him.

00:19:42.160 --> 00:19:49.270
He is the vine. I am the branch. I can do nothing outside of him.

00:19:49.271 --> 00:19:55.839
And so many people—if Jesus couldn't do it, how much more could we?

00:19:55.840 --> 00:20:05.006
How arrogant—the Son of God could do nothing without hearing what his father told him to do.

00:20:05.007 --> 00:20:15.918
I do nothing unless I'm instructed by my Lord. And Jesus was dead to himself. You know, that's what I have for you today.

00:20:15.919 --> 00:20:25.678
I feel I just want you to understand there's a place in God that the devil is afraid even to go.

00:20:25.679 --> 00:20:34.879
There's a place in God—Smith Wigglesworth talked about this—there is a place in God that Satan dare not go.

00:20:34.880 --> 00:20:43.255
He's scared of it. That's where I want to be. I want to be right at his feet.

00:20:43.256 --> 00:20:53.950
I want to be sitting at his feet, listening to him, listening to that still small voice—the still small voice of my good shepherd.

00:20:53.951 --> 00:21:02.872
I am the sheep and I am on that potter's wheel, even feeling it, "Well, there's a level of success.

00:21:02.873 --> 00:21:15.834
There's a level of this."It's all nothing without him. I don't care how anointed a prayer session is and the glory shows up—without him, he is that.

00:21:15.835 --> 00:21:25.359
But even then, I've seen some of the greatest ministers move under the anointing for just a part of that time. He shows up just to set the captives free.

00:21:25.360 --> 00:21:34.239
Just because you have an anointed service, an anointed time with the Lord, doesn't mean he truly knows you all the way.

00:21:34.240 --> 00:21:42.257
It doesn't. He can use whoever he wants just to get the job done because he loves the people.

00:21:42.258 --> 00:21:48.399
But whenever it's all said and done and the lights are off, I can turn them all off.

00:21:48.400 --> 00:21:59.353
Is he still there? Is he there whenever nobody else is watching? Who are you whenever the camera is not rolling?

00:21:59.354 --> 00:22:05.746
Who are you whenever you are sitting on the back row and you're watching and observing?

00:22:05.747 --> 00:22:12.219
Do you know how many times the Lord will reveal to me more—and I'm nothing special.

00:22:12.220 --> 00:22:16.505
I'll be real with you. I just walk in a gift. I just walk in a gift.

00:22:16.506 --> 00:22:25.353
How many times he shows up and he tells me, "Brandon, they have issues. Be careful with them.

00:22:25.354 --> 00:22:34.798
Don't allow them in your inner circle."What is he saying about you to other people whenever he is warning them about you?

00:22:34.799 --> 00:22:43.374
Do you see what I'm saying? He has an opinion about everything. What is his opinion about you?

00:22:43.375 --> 00:22:47.699
I question what people see about me from Billy Burke when they get around you.

00:22:47.700 --> 00:22:54.469
If they walk in any discernment, do they see anything bad? Everybody has a sense of something.

00:22:54.470 --> 00:23:07.429
For instance, my wife said lust has a feeling, and if a man has something bad, a woman can feel it whenever that man's looking at her.

00:23:07.430 --> 00:23:14.954
She says, "Oh, he's undressing me with his eyes."You see that? There is a spirit of lust that people carry.

00:23:14.955 --> 00:23:20.098
But you can be saturated enough, you can carry the Lord, and people can sense it on you.

00:23:20.099 --> 00:23:25.272
What do you carry? What is on you enough that people can sense it on you?

00:23:25.273 --> 00:23:33.436
Some people have gossip, some people have lust, some people have greed, some people have jealousy. Jealousy is stinky.

00:23:33.437 --> 00:23:44.525
You can sense it when somebody's jealous of what God's doing in your life and they don't feel like you deserve what you have and they feel they could do it better than you.

00:23:44.526 --> 00:23:49.759
And when they see you, they detest you. And you can feel that.

00:23:49.760 --> 00:23:55.038
You can feel that energy. You can feel that badness of what they're carrying.

00:23:55.039 --> 00:24:08.319
When you just get around them, you can tell they feel that you don't deserve what you have or the anointing where God's put you, and they feel because of where they're at that they could do it so much better.

00:24:08.320 --> 00:24:14.034
I have that all the time. I sense it all the time. I sense it in church. I sense it all the time.

00:24:14.034 --> 00:24:20.200
Maybe even with people that you would least expect it, but it's there.

00:24:20.201 --> 00:24:33.038
What do people sense about you? It's like that. Like I just said, there's some guys—he just hugs way too long.

00:24:33.039 --> 00:24:38.079
He's a little bit too familiar with the other ladies. Do you see?

00:24:38.080 --> 00:24:45.439
What do people sense about you? What do you carry? What do you carry about you?

00:24:45.440 --> 00:24:52.079
And that's why I always self-examine myself. What do people see about Brandon?

00:24:52.080 --> 00:24:55.760
